title: Da Baby Interview and More
itunes:title: Da Baby Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had rapper Da Baby stop by where he spoke about his new album "Kirk" , his support team and family, security fighting and more. Also, since Charlmagne was not here today we let the listeners get a chance to give "Donkey of the Day" to anyone they think deserves the hee- haw and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
